data.description: Pride of Ownership shows in this Very Well Maintained 3 Bed, 2 Bath 1710 Single Level Home built in 1993. Family Room, Granite Counter tops in kitchen and Island. Den could easily be an additional bedroom. A/C Replaced in 2021. New Hot Water Heater in 2021. Both Bathrooms Updated 8 months ago. Air Ducts Cleaned 1 years ago. Inside laundry. Plantation Shutters Throughout the Home. Large Covered Patio. Beautiful Backyard! One of the Sellers is a Licensed Realtor in the State of Arizona.
